Invocation Name: medicine woman
des:
Listen to this timeless story from the Hachi Tribe, the story of the inner medicine woman in me, I call her Ekoina, every time I hug a tree and place my ear to it, I thank her for the medicine, the sacred knowledge of my tribe.
Discover the inner medicine circle, when in the woods, listen to nature and discover the true medicine.
